ED street lights; and drive products. In addition, the company offers mini, monobloc, openwell submersible, borewell waterfilled and oilfield submersible, jet, vacuum, and industrial pumps, as well as fire fighting systems; and vertical multistage inline centrifugal, horizontal centrifugal, end-suction centrifugal close coupled, horizontal split case, single-stage long coupled end-suction, high pressure vertical multistage inline, submerged centrifugal, multi stage multi outlet fire, end suction fire, self priming, and chemical thermoplastic centrifugal pumps; electrical control panel; and cable and wire products. Further, it provides services and support, and motor rewinding services. It serves textile, material handling, chemical and pharmaceutical, solvent plants, flour mills, food processing, dairy and cattle feed, sugar, distillery, paper and particle board, steel, forging, cement, and crusher and mining industries. The company was founded in 2002 and is based in Surat, India."}}